WEBVTT

00:17.960 --> 00:19.000
This letter

00:19.760 --> 00:23.000
was written by Consort Qi
to Wei Yan, pleading for help.

00:23.640 --> 00:25.280
Because of a private affair,

00:25.800 --> 00:27.240
Wei Yan returned to the capital midway,

00:27.960 --> 00:30.080
leaving the soldiers of Jinzhou
to face the enemy alone.

00:30.640 --> 00:31.520
In the end,

00:31.600 --> 00:32.960
it led directly to that great catastrophe.

00:33.040 --> 00:34.640
…I KNOW YOU ARE TRAPPED IN JINZHOU…
THE CONSPIRATORS' SCHEME RUNS DEEP…

00:34.720 --> 00:36.400
FATHER AND BROTHER ARE TRAPPED, YET I AM
CONFINED IN THE PALACE. I BEG YOUR AID…

00:38.560 --> 00:40.160
A thief crying thief.

00:41.520 --> 00:42.480
Wei Yan,

00:43.880 --> 00:46.400
you are the true traitor
behind the disaster at Jinzhou!

00:47.520 --> 00:48.680
This is Qi Rongyin's letter.

00:49.360 --> 00:52.240
After 17 years, you've probably forgotten.

00:53.200 --> 00:54.360
Let me read it for you.

00:55.480 --> 00:56.440
"To my Yan,

00:56.520 --> 00:58.320
-when you read this, imagine me--"
-Silence!

00:59.600 --> 01:01.720
Wei Changyu,
if you want to fight, then fight.

01:01.800 --> 01:04.519
Do not defile the honor
of a woman long gone.

01:06.720 --> 01:09.000
It seems there are still people
the Chancellor cares about.

01:09.080 --> 01:10.800
Seventeen years ago,

01:11.760 --> 01:13.400
my mother hid this letter

01:14.320 --> 01:16.480
in the candy box you gave her.

01:17.000 --> 01:18.480
All these years,

01:19.200 --> 01:22.000
you've committed every evil.
That's why your conscience pricks you so.

01:22.080 --> 01:23.640
You don't dare to touch that candy box.

01:25.000 --> 01:26.120
Let me ask you, Chancellor,

01:26.960 --> 01:28.280
in these 17 years,

01:29.080 --> 01:30.840
have you ever repented to my father?

01:31.720 --> 01:33.200
Have you ever pitied

01:33.720 --> 01:35.400
the thousands of fallen soldiers?

01:36.040 --> 01:37.560
Have you ever mourned

01:37.640 --> 01:39.080
your own sister,
who took her own life desperately?

01:42.280 --> 01:43.720
A forged letter

01:44.320 --> 01:45.520
and a pair of counterfeit tiger tallies,

01:46.120 --> 01:48.000
and you think that's enough to smear me?

01:49.720 --> 01:51.200
Given this letter, Chancellor,

01:51.720 --> 01:53.280
how many people have you silenced?

01:54.080 --> 01:55.760
If Consort Qi could see your evil deeds

01:55.840 --> 01:56.760
-from the underworld--
-Silence!

01:57.760 --> 01:59.160
Don't you mention her!

02:04.400 --> 02:07.200
To confirm the authenticity
of these tiger tallies

02:07.280 --> 02:08.120
isn't difficult.

02:08.720 --> 02:10.199
Tiger tallies are sacred
instrument of state.

02:10.280 --> 02:11.680
The Ministry of War keeps records.

02:12.280 --> 02:13.720
Though the archives have been burned,

02:14.280 --> 02:16.160
the man who forged the tallies back then,

02:16.240 --> 02:18.560
Grand Tutor Tao, is still alive.

02:18.640 --> 02:20.680
The Chancellor need only ask him.

02:23.040 --> 02:25.440
Grand Tutor Tao has arrived.

02:32.080 --> 02:34.240
I kowtow to Your Majesty.

02:34.320 --> 02:35.720
Rise.

02:35.800 --> 02:37.280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

02:38.200 --> 02:41.360
Grand Tutor Tao is one
of the few witnesses from back then.

02:41.880 --> 02:43.720
To preserve the royal family's honor,

02:44.480 --> 02:46.280
I ask you to examine
these military tallies

02:46.360 --> 02:48.040
and determine whether they are genuine.

02:48.120 --> 02:49.640
I obey the decree.

02:58.320 --> 02:59.720
TIGER TALLY

03:04.640 --> 03:06.000
Reporting to Your Majesty.

03:06.080 --> 03:09.720
Back then, I personally supervised
the forging of these military tallies.

03:10.360 --> 03:12.600
These marks confirm it.

03:12.680 --> 03:15.080
This is genuine.

03:17.960 --> 03:18.800
Chancellor Wei.

03:20.360 --> 03:22.000
What do you have to say for yourself now?

03:31.320 --> 03:33.640
You'll be empress soon.

03:37.560 --> 03:40.120
Wei Yan, your ambition knows no bounds,

03:40.200 --> 03:41.240
deceiving both ruler and heaven.

03:41.320 --> 03:42.360
Your crime deserves death.

03:43.120 --> 03:44.600
-Imperial Guards!
-Here!

03:44.680 --> 03:46.560
-Seize him!
-Yes, sir!

04:06.280 --> 04:07.760
Wei Yan, you…

04:10.840 --> 04:12.520
You little Qi brat,

04:13.160 --> 04:15.080
do you dare?

04:18.040 --> 04:20.880
Yigui, don't repeat your mistakes!

04:28.880 --> 04:29.920
Report!

04:31.000 --> 04:32.080
Your Majesty, terrible news!

04:32.680 --> 04:33.760
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai

04:33.840 --> 04:35.360
and his army are storming
through the Dayin Gate!

04:36.040 --> 04:37.000
What?

04:40.960 --> 04:42.120
How did they break in?

04:47.840 --> 04:49.200
This day has finally come.

04:51.040 --> 04:52.920
He really knows how to pick his days.

04:59.120 --> 05:01.120
The score between us

05:01.720 --> 05:03.000
must be settled.

05:03.520 --> 05:05.400
But before that,

05:06.040 --> 05:08.240
let me quell this rebellion first.

05:09.840 --> 05:10.920
Let's go.

06:41.920 --> 06:46.920
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

06:50.800 --> 06:52.160
All of you.

06:52.680 --> 06:53.680
Kill for me!

07:05.520 --> 07:08.840
DAYIN GATE

07:37.480 --> 07:39.880
Welcoming the true master
back to the palace.

07:40.920 --> 07:43.160
Welcoming the true master
back to the palace.

07:43.680 --> 07:46.040
Welcoming the true master
back to the palace.

07:46.640 --> 07:48.720
Welcoming the true master
back to the palace.

08:11.240 --> 08:13.520
Welcoming the true master
back to the palace.

08:21.680 --> 08:23.120
Seventeen years.

08:23.200 --> 08:26.360
I've finally reclaimed
what is rightfully mine.

08:29.720 --> 08:31.680
Your Highness ascending
the throne once more,

08:31.760 --> 08:33.720
truly heaven's will made manifest.

08:33.799 --> 08:35.720
The mandate of heaven is yours.

08:35.799 --> 08:37.360
The mandate of heaven is yours.

08:42.960 --> 08:43.919
Qianqian,

08:45.880 --> 08:46.800
how about that?

08:47.680 --> 08:49.240
The promise I made you,

08:50.280 --> 08:51.400
I've kept it.

08:52.040 --> 08:53.600
You madman.

08:55.480 --> 08:57.600
Did you really think
I wanted to be your empress?

08:58.880 --> 09:00.040
Dream on.

09:07.640 --> 09:09.280
You'll agree to me.

09:20.480 --> 09:21.440
Little brother Sheng,

09:22.600 --> 09:25.600
you've sat in this seat for over a decade.

09:26.720 --> 09:28.440
Has it been comfortable?

09:44.400 --> 09:45.360
Imperial Brother,

09:45.880 --> 09:46.920
I…

09:49.360 --> 09:51.040
I've been waiting here for you so long.

09:52.960 --> 09:54.160
The imperial seal is here.

09:55.720 --> 09:57.520
It's all yours.

10:10.840 --> 10:13.400
I beg you,
Imperial Brother, don't kill me.

10:14.440 --> 10:15.880
Please don't kill me.

10:18.720 --> 10:21.760
With you, such a useless fool
as the Emperor of Dayin,

10:21.840 --> 10:23.040
do you think that makes up

10:23.120 --> 10:25.560
for the suffering
I've endured all these years?

10:26.560 --> 10:28.920
I…

10:33.720 --> 10:34.840
Take him away.

10:34.920 --> 10:36.080
Await judgment.

10:36.720 --> 10:37.760
Yes.

10:39.480 --> 10:40.320
Don't kill me.

10:41.400 --> 10:42.280
Don't kill me.

10:42.800 --> 10:43.840
Don't kill me.

10:47.560 --> 10:48.480
Don't kill me.

10:52.680 --> 10:54.760
Is he really going to be the Emperor?

10:57.320 --> 10:59.480
Report! Unusual movement near Xuan Gate.

10:59.560 --> 11:00.840
Reinforcements may approach
from outside the palace.

11:34.480 --> 11:36.280
Damn. It's a trap.

11:42.960 --> 11:46.600
Li Xing conspired with the rebel
Sui Yuanhuai, plotting treason.

11:47.280 --> 11:49.320
Such traitors to the state

11:49.920 --> 11:52.360
shall all be apprehended
and brought to justice.

11:53.800 --> 11:55.200
You Wei scoundrel,

11:55.280 --> 11:56.520
don't think for a moment

11:56.600 --> 11:58.680
that with this meager force

11:58.760 --> 12:01.320
you can stop His Highness's Five Armies.

12:20.640 --> 12:21.880
Isn't this enough?

12:23.600 --> 12:24.880
This meager force?

12:26.160 --> 12:28.680
Besides, we don't yet know who will

12:28.760 --> 12:30.640
the Marquis of Wu'an's be side with.

12:32.400 --> 12:35.280
Marquis of Wu'an,
since you've come to join the fun,

12:35.880 --> 12:37.360
why not cooperate with me?

12:38.440 --> 12:41.240
I've already detained that puppet emperor.

12:41.800 --> 12:43.400
Throw in your lot with me.

12:43.480 --> 12:46.160
After all, I am the true bloodline
of Crown Prince Chengde.

12:49.080 --> 12:50.120
Qi Min,

12:50.680 --> 12:52.360
you secretly colluded
with the Northern Jue,

12:52.880 --> 12:55.240
intending to use this chance
to bring down Dayin.

12:55.840 --> 12:57.320
Did you really think I wouldn't notice?

12:58.240 --> 12:59.920
You claim to be
Crown Prince Chengde's heir,

13:00.000 --> 13:03.440
yet you forget the former Eastern Palace
died fighting the North.

13:03.960 --> 13:05.560
I, Xie Zheng,

13:05.640 --> 13:07.120
how could I ever serve you?

13:07.200 --> 13:08.560
What?

13:10.800 --> 13:13.240
You dared to collude
with the Northern Jue in secret,

13:13.320 --> 13:16.440
handing Dayin's land over to barbarians?

13:16.960 --> 13:18.680
An arrow once loosed never returns.

13:19.280 --> 13:22.280
Grand Tutor Li,
it's far too late for regrets now.

13:22.360 --> 13:23.200
You…

13:24.440 --> 13:27.800
What Chancellor Wei did
was far worse than me.

13:29.040 --> 13:31.480
Jinzhou fell, its people slaughtered,

13:32.080 --> 13:34.760
12 prefectures of Liaodong
ceded to the barbarians.

13:35.520 --> 13:37.400
All because Wei Yan,

13:37.480 --> 13:40.680
in his greed for Dayin's land,
brought it about with his own hand.

13:41.200 --> 13:43.640
I'm merely finishing

13:43.720 --> 13:45.040
what he left undone.

13:45.720 --> 13:46.560
You…

13:50.840 --> 13:51.920
Chancellor Wei,

13:53.080 --> 13:54.560
17 years ago,

13:55.080 --> 13:56.760
you bathed the palace in blood.

13:57.280 --> 13:59.680
Did you really think no one knew

13:59.760 --> 14:01.800
of your defilement of the harem?

14:02.400 --> 14:05.120
You bastard, impersonating royal blood,

14:05.640 --> 14:09.360
and still here spouting lies,
fabricating facts.

14:09.960 --> 14:11.720
Who's spouting lies?

14:11.800 --> 14:14.880
You know better than anyone,
Wei Yan, don't you?

14:16.240 --> 14:17.400
Seize him!

14:17.960 --> 14:20.760
Every traitor present today,

14:20.840 --> 14:22.480
kill them all with no mercy!

14:33.960 --> 14:35.960
Chancellor Wei, look.

14:36.480 --> 14:38.120
Your wife and son are here.

14:38.200 --> 14:40.920
I guarantee,
if any of your men dare step forward,

14:41.000 --> 14:42.960
their heads will roll.

14:55.000 --> 14:57.360
I never expected the Chancellor
to be so cold-blooded.

14:58.000 --> 15:01.000
Then let you wife and son

15:01.600 --> 15:03.560
descend to hell first.

15:20.440 --> 15:21.320
Kill them!

15:21.400 --> 15:22.240
Kill!

15:38.880 --> 15:39.880
Don't kill me.

15:39.960 --> 15:40.960
Don't kill me.

15:41.960 --> 15:42.840
Don't kill me.

15:42.920 --> 15:44.160
Don't kill me.

15:44.240 --> 15:46.480
I'll make you great generals,
alright? Please?

15:47.320 --> 15:50.080
Another word and I'll cut you down.

15:51.600 --> 15:53.400
Time to end this.

15:54.360 --> 15:55.200
Chancellor.

15:57.320 --> 15:59.720
This is between uncle and nephew.

16:01.520 --> 16:02.920
None of you interfere. Step back.

17:02.920 --> 17:05.119
Your swordsmanship
has improved quite a bit.

17:06.440 --> 17:08.359
I'll use my father's swordsmanship

17:09.000 --> 17:10.880
to seek justice
for my parents and Changyu's,

17:11.520 --> 17:13.800
for the former Eastern Palace,
for every soldier

17:14.640 --> 17:15.839
who died in Jinzhou.

17:17.359 --> 17:18.319
Good.

17:19.200 --> 17:20.200
Come on, then.

17:48.440 --> 17:49.640
Give up.

17:50.200 --> 17:51.200
What is not yours,

17:52.080 --> 17:53.520
you'll never have it.

17:59.000 --> 18:00.880
This realm was always mine to begin with.

18:01.640 --> 18:02.920
Always mine.

18:05.600 --> 18:06.440
Do you like it?

18:07.520 --> 18:08.760
Do you?

18:09.920 --> 18:11.680
It's so hard… I don't want it anymore.

18:17.120 --> 18:19.880
Being emperor is too hard.

18:28.480 --> 18:30.840
I don't want to be emperor.

18:31.880 --> 18:33.640
I don't want it.

18:41.760 --> 18:43.080
You've truly lost your mind!

18:43.680 --> 18:44.960
I haven't lost my mind.

18:45.880 --> 18:48.120
I chose to live because of you.

18:48.200 --> 18:49.480
For me?

18:51.000 --> 18:51.920
Fine.

18:52.960 --> 18:54.600
If I die, you'll stop being mad.

18:59.280 --> 19:01.600
I won't allow you to die.

19:04.120 --> 19:06.000
Qi Min. Let Qian go.

19:08.200 --> 19:09.120
Changyu,

19:09.760 --> 19:11.000
don't worry about me.

19:11.520 --> 19:12.640
I can't escape.

19:42.240 --> 19:43.400
Let her go!

19:43.480 --> 19:45.240
Or I'll kill you!

19:47.120 --> 19:48.040
Changyu,

19:48.640 --> 19:49.960
let go.

19:50.600 --> 19:52.560
What's between us
shouldn't drag you into it.

19:56.720 --> 19:58.040
I wanted the throne,

19:59.080 --> 20:00.120
and I wanted you.

20:01.440 --> 20:02.440
But in the end,

20:03.240 --> 20:04.640
I'm left with nothing.

20:04.720 --> 20:07.840
Let go. You'll get her killed!

20:13.160 --> 20:15.000
He won't let go.

20:19.040 --> 20:21.440
He's never learnt to let go.

20:30.640 --> 20:34.080
You're selfish, brutal, and moody.

20:35.120 --> 20:36.800
It's all just an act.

20:37.320 --> 20:39.960
You're only hiding your own fear.

20:40.920 --> 20:42.680
You're just pitiful.

20:43.200 --> 20:45.320
Is my love so worthless,

20:45.400 --> 20:46.720
only fit for you to trample on?

20:47.240 --> 20:48.240
That's not love.

20:48.960 --> 20:50.920
It's possessiveness! It's control!

20:52.240 --> 20:54.000
I don't want any of it.

20:54.760 --> 20:56.560
I just want to leave you forever.

21:02.000 --> 21:02.960
For you…

21:05.240 --> 21:06.840
I'm willing to learn.

23:08.800 --> 23:09.840
Xuan.

23:11.400 --> 23:12.840
Xuan!

23:14.000 --> 23:15.320
I took this one

23:17.000 --> 23:19.560
to repay you for saving my mother.

23:24.160 --> 23:25.000
You are

23:25.760 --> 23:28.160
not my father, you bastard.

23:35.520 --> 23:36.680
Xuan!

24:16.800 --> 24:18.160
XIE, MARQUIS WU'AN

24:20.000 --> 24:21.960
The Jizhou army
and the Xie army have arrived.

24:22.480 --> 24:23.480
The Forbidden Palace is secure.

24:24.120 --> 24:26.880
All soldiers following Qi
and Wei in rebellion, listen to me.

24:27.480 --> 24:29.360
Those who lay down
your weapons and surrender,

24:29.960 --> 24:30.880
your lives could be spared.

24:31.880 --> 24:32.960
Those who resist

24:33.760 --> 24:35.600
will be charged with treason,

24:36.200 --> 24:37.440
and your entire clans exterminated.

24:39.800 --> 24:40.880
Chancellor,

24:41.720 --> 24:43.000
your army has fallen.

24:43.720 --> 24:45.480
Still trying to struggle?

24:49.120 --> 24:50.400
Jiuheng,

24:52.000 --> 24:54.080
you haven't let me down.

24:57.480 --> 24:58.480
Chancellor.

25:00.760 --> 25:03.360
Let's retreat. We'll escort you out.

25:08.200 --> 25:09.240
No.

25:12.120 --> 25:13.200
Lost…

25:14.080 --> 25:15.160
is lost.

25:15.680 --> 25:18.880
Seventeen years ago,
when I set foot on this path of no return,

25:20.360 --> 25:21.840
this day, this end,

25:23.560 --> 25:25.320
was already written.

25:33.840 --> 25:34.680
Take him away.

25:36.880 --> 25:38.000
Let's go, Chancellor.

26:11.680 --> 26:12.840
It's over.

26:16.480 --> 26:17.800
It's all over…

26:20.280 --> 26:21.560
just like that.

26:24.840 --> 26:25.840
It's over.

26:29.640 --> 26:31.600
Our lives together
will be better from now on.

26:35.520 --> 26:37.160
If there really is an afterlife,

26:38.760 --> 26:39.880
let me be the one to find you.

27:18.240 --> 27:22.320
THREE DAYS LATER

27:37.880 --> 27:39.760
Marquis, Lady Wei has arrived.

27:41.240 --> 27:42.640
My lady, please.

27:48.320 --> 27:49.280
Aunt.

27:51.360 --> 27:52.520
Zheng.

27:56.200 --> 27:57.040
Aunt.

27:58.320 --> 28:00.200
What's the meaning of this?
Get up, quickly.

28:00.720 --> 28:01.640
Zheng.

28:02.360 --> 28:05.520
I beg you to spare the Chancellor's life.

28:11.600 --> 28:12.640
Please, sit first.

28:18.320 --> 28:19.160
Aunt.

28:20.680 --> 28:22.640
He didn't even care
about you and your son's lives.

28:22.720 --> 28:24.640
Why plead for him?

28:25.280 --> 28:27.440
Besides, the law of the land
cannot be defied.

28:30.040 --> 28:33.120
The Chancellor is not beyond redemption.

28:34.360 --> 28:35.640
Without him,

28:36.240 --> 28:39.040
Xuan and I would have died long ago.

28:41.640 --> 28:42.800
What do you mean by that?

28:43.840 --> 28:45.360
Xuan's father

28:45.880 --> 28:47.680
was one of the Chancellor's men.

28:48.840 --> 28:51.600
His father and I pledged ourselves
to each other in secret,

28:52.640 --> 28:54.960
but he died on the battlefield.

28:56.040 --> 28:57.240
My family

28:57.320 --> 28:59.560
wanted to drag me back
and drown me in a pig cage.

29:00.800 --> 29:02.880
The Chancellor saved me.

29:04.840 --> 29:06.040
He said

29:06.560 --> 29:09.400
Xuan's father was his old subordinate.

29:10.320 --> 29:14.080
He never planned to marry,

29:14.720 --> 29:16.920
but his family kept pressing him.

29:17.760 --> 29:20.600
I was desperate, carrying a child,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.560
with nowhere to go.

29:23.280 --> 29:25.800
He said it was a solution
that worked for both.

29:29.320 --> 29:31.720
The Chancellor's kindness to us…

29:33.720 --> 29:35.400
It's as heavy as a mountain.

29:37.240 --> 29:38.080
Zheng,

29:39.080 --> 29:42.040
I beg you, for Xuan's sake,
for that arrow he took for you,

29:42.680 --> 29:44.640
please spare the Chancellor's life.

29:49.000 --> 29:49.840
Aunt,

29:50.960 --> 29:52.280
did he never marry

29:53.160 --> 29:54.600
because of Imperial Consort Qi?

29:58.680 --> 30:01.000
The Chancellor's heart runs deep.

30:01.640 --> 30:02.640
I don't know.

30:25.360 --> 30:26.320
Zheng,

30:27.640 --> 30:29.600
if the law truly cannot be bent,

30:30.200 --> 30:33.680
I beg you, for the sake
of your bond as uncle and nephew,

30:35.440 --> 30:37.080
let the Chancellor keep his body whole.

30:50.400 --> 30:52.520
The Flower-Adorned General has arrived.

30:58.120 --> 31:00.120
CASTING OFF SPLENDOR

31:00.200 --> 31:01.160
Changyu!

31:02.400 --> 31:04.440
How are you? Are your wounds okay?

31:04.960 --> 31:05.800
I'm fine.

31:06.400 --> 31:07.280
Come here.

31:08.800 --> 31:09.680
Mother.

31:11.440 --> 31:12.360
Empress Dowager.

31:16.040 --> 31:17.120
Mother.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.520
Wei Yan is captured.

31:22.560 --> 31:24.120
My brother is lost to madness.

31:25.080 --> 31:26.680
The world has already changed.

31:27.200 --> 31:30.440
What purpose does your silence serve now?

31:34.320 --> 31:36.160
The world did change.

31:36.920 --> 31:40.120
It has changed since 17 years ago.

31:42.560 --> 31:45.160
When Imperial Consort Qi
first entered the palace,

31:45.680 --> 31:47.920
she was a woman of extreme reserve,

31:48.640 --> 31:50.640
never vying for the emperor's favor.

31:50.720 --> 31:51.440
QIYI, THE LATE EMPEROR

31:52.160 --> 31:54.160
Not until she was found with child.

31:54.800 --> 31:57.720
The imperial physician
determined the month of conception

31:57.800 --> 32:00.560
didn't match the records
of the Palace Domestic Service.

32:04.520 --> 32:07.040
Did Consort Qi
really have an affair with Wei Yan?

32:07.640 --> 32:09.600
Qi Rongyin was three months pregnant.

32:10.120 --> 32:11.680
Counting backward,

32:12.600 --> 32:15.040
the conception would have been
around the Mid-Autumn Festival.

32:15.960 --> 32:17.600
That year at the palace banquet,

32:19.200 --> 32:21.440
Wei Yan got drunk,

32:22.200 --> 32:25.360
lost control, and violated a palace maid.

32:25.880 --> 32:28.000
By ill chance,
the late emperor and his ministers

32:28.080 --> 32:30.280
happened upon the scene
while admiring the moon.

32:32.400 --> 32:34.560
A mere maid.

32:35.520 --> 32:37.800
The late emperor couldn't
make a scene then and there.

32:39.000 --> 32:42.200
So he bestowed the maid upon Wei Yan.

32:43.600 --> 32:45.240
The royal house knows no mercy.

32:46.280 --> 32:48.760
After Consort Qi was found with child,

32:49.800 --> 32:51.360
she was interrogated night after night.

32:52.360 --> 32:53.920
Until that night,

32:54.000 --> 32:56.600
when Qingyuan Palace suddenly caught fire.

32:57.320 --> 32:57.920
Minister Wei.

32:58.000 --> 32:59.760
-The Imperial Guards on patrol
-Now scram!

32:59.840 --> 33:01.120
rushed to put out the fire…

33:01.200 --> 33:02.040
QINGYUAN PALACE

33:02.120 --> 33:03.400
…and discovered Wei Yan,

33:03.920 --> 33:05.280
without summons,

33:06.000 --> 33:07.720
had entered the Forbidden Palace.

33:07.800 --> 33:08.920
Get out!

33:09.000 --> 33:10.600
Zhao Xun once testified

33:11.400 --> 33:14.440
that the palace fire was set
by Crown Princess Chengde.

33:15.240 --> 33:16.760
Could there be more to it?

33:18.280 --> 33:21.600
Have you ever seen water poured on a fire,

33:22.360 --> 33:24.280
only to make the flames leap higher?

33:24.880 --> 33:26.120
I have.

33:26.720 --> 33:29.120
That fire reeked of tung oil.

33:29.640 --> 33:30.920
The palace was surrounded.

33:31.000 --> 33:32.840
The roar of slaughter filled the sky,

33:33.680 --> 33:35.200
just like the other day.

33:36.840 --> 33:39.480
Later, the imperial physician
who examined her took his own life.

33:39.560 --> 33:40.680
In his suicide note, he wrote

33:40.760 --> 33:43.320
that Consort Qi
had never been pregnant at all.

33:43.840 --> 33:47.240
So, the one who set the fire
was Crown Princess Chengde.

33:47.320 --> 33:49.080
And the one who burned Consort Qi to death

33:49.880 --> 33:50.960
was the late Emperor.

34:00.360 --> 34:01.800
Thank you, Empress Dowager,

34:02.400 --> 34:04.080
for sharing this piece of history.

34:37.920 --> 34:41.320
Jiuheng, you've come to see
your uncle off on his final journey?

34:42.800 --> 34:44.800
I have come to finish

34:44.880 --> 34:47.159
that unfinished game
of Go Chess with you, Chancellor.

34:52.440 --> 34:56.480
That boy's father, General Xie,
died horribly in Jinzhou.

34:56.560 --> 34:58.400
The truth back in the days,

34:58.480 --> 35:00.840
he absolutely will not let it slide.

35:05.640 --> 35:08.040
It was the late Emperor who set the trap.

35:08.120 --> 35:11.360
So why did you take
the blame all these years?

35:11.440 --> 35:12.880
What did you gain from it?

35:26.920 --> 35:28.240
This game of Go,

35:29.040 --> 35:31.320
surely you're quite familiar
with it, Chancellor?

35:58.320 --> 35:59.440
Have you made up your mind?

35:59.520 --> 36:00.760
If not,

36:01.280 --> 36:02.720
will you allow me to rest a while longer?

36:04.160 --> 36:06.200
Yan, you're cheating!

36:07.000 --> 36:09.480
You said you'd use only 30%
of your skill to keep me entertained.

36:10.000 --> 36:11.200
This is clearly

36:11.720 --> 36:13.360
a full-force encirclement
and interception.

36:13.440 --> 36:16.040
I really did only use 30%.

36:16.640 --> 36:18.000
Then just say it outright.

36:18.520 --> 36:20.480
I am not a good player,
and I'm no match for you.

36:21.440 --> 36:22.760
I quit.

36:24.960 --> 36:27.040
Fine. Let me retract one move.

36:27.560 --> 36:29.240
Let me think carefully

36:29.320 --> 36:33.120
how to lose gracefully
while using only 30%.

36:36.520 --> 36:37.960
Losing at Go isn't hard.

36:38.040 --> 36:39.600
Let me give you a hand, brother.

36:39.680 --> 36:40.640
Little sister, stop.

36:41.560 --> 36:43.480
Brother, you blockhead.

36:43.560 --> 36:46.400
Be careful. If you keep winning,
you'll scare my sister-in-law away.

36:48.520 --> 36:50.640
Wan said you were playing Go here.

36:50.720 --> 36:53.440
I thought I'd join the fun.

36:53.520 --> 36:54.920
No need for formalities.

36:55.000 --> 36:56.720
Sit.

37:01.680 --> 37:04.800
When a piece falls into
an isolated, unsupported position,

37:04.880 --> 37:08.200
you must quickly find a way
to bring it back to life.

37:17.920 --> 37:20.080
This game of Go, like life itself,

37:20.600 --> 37:22.120
there must be giving and taking.

37:25.120 --> 37:26.800
"This game of Go, like life itself,

37:27.320 --> 37:28.560
there must be giving and taking."

37:30.960 --> 37:31.880
Grand Tutor,

37:32.400 --> 37:33.960
those were your words.

37:35.040 --> 37:36.480
At this point,

37:37.640 --> 37:39.880
no more riddles with me.

37:39.960 --> 37:41.760
I never believed

37:42.280 --> 37:44.720
you orchestrated the Jinzhou tragedy.

37:45.920 --> 37:49.240
But why did you rush back
to the capital back then?

37:50.320 --> 37:52.040
What really happened?

37:53.640 --> 37:56.680
Remember the New Year's Eve banquet
18 years ago,

37:57.760 --> 38:00.000
the osmanthus wine feast
at the Eastern Palace?

38:01.800 --> 38:04.840
Grand Tutor, you were there too.

38:06.520 --> 38:09.760
That night, young and reckless,

38:10.560 --> 38:13.000
I planted the seeds of disaster
with my careless words.

38:13.080 --> 38:16.880
THE FIFTEENTH YEAR OF QISHUN

38:21.560 --> 38:22.760
Tonight, New Year's Eve,

38:23.280 --> 38:24.600
I've specially invited you all

38:24.680 --> 38:28.120
to taste the osmanthus wine
brewed right here in the Eastern Palace.

38:28.200 --> 38:29.960
Fine wine in the cold of winter,

38:30.040 --> 38:31.000
roasted venison on the fire…

38:31.080 --> 38:31.720
QI YUAN, CROWN PRINCE CHENGDE

38:31.800 --> 38:32.960
Could there be greater pleasure?

38:33.480 --> 38:34.640
LI JING, CHANCELLOR OF IMPERIAL ACADEMY
TAO YI, MINISTER OF WORKS

38:34.720 --> 38:35.600
Thank you.

38:36.120 --> 38:37.360
This osmanthus wine,

38:37.440 --> 38:38.560
its rich fragrance fills the air.

38:38.640 --> 38:39.320
WEI YAN, CENTRAL COMMANDER
XIE LINSHAN, PROTECTOR GENERAL OF REALM

38:39.400 --> 38:40.240
Truly a fine brew.

38:40.320 --> 38:41.600
Come, Your Highness the Crown Prince,

38:41.680 --> 38:42.520
allow me to offer you another toast.

38:42.600 --> 38:44.040
General Xie.

38:44.120 --> 38:46.400
Tonight, have you been given permission

38:46.480 --> 38:47.920
to drink your fill?

38:48.440 --> 38:50.680
I suggest you take it easy.

38:50.760 --> 38:53.600
Leave a little
for the rest of us to savor, hm?

38:54.840 --> 38:56.920
The Commander speaks truly.

38:57.440 --> 38:59.200
Linshan can drink like a fish.

38:59.280 --> 39:01.160
If you don't restrain yourself,

39:01.240 --> 39:03.720
the rest of us will have none left.

39:03.800 --> 39:05.600
-You…
-Grand Tutor.

39:05.680 --> 39:07.600
It's only osmanthus wine.

39:07.680 --> 39:09.080
As long as you all enjoy it,

39:09.600 --> 39:10.520
there's plenty to go around.

39:10.600 --> 39:11.720
Excellent.

39:12.560 --> 39:14.160
-Drink up!
-We've got wine to drink!

39:14.240 --> 39:15.640
-Come.
-Drink up.

39:18.040 --> 39:19.680
Fine wine, good food,

39:19.760 --> 39:21.120
loyal ministers, a wise ruler,

39:21.200 --> 39:22.560
friends to share it with.

39:22.640 --> 39:25.200
This is the greatest pleasure in life.

39:25.280 --> 39:26.200
Qilin,

39:26.280 --> 39:30.000
this may be the last time
we keep the vigil together.

39:30.720 --> 39:32.200
I'm leaving the capital soon…

39:32.280 --> 39:33.120
HE JINGYUAN,
GENERAL MILITARY ADMINISTRATOR

39:33.200 --> 39:34.160
…bound for Jinzhou.

39:34.240 --> 39:35.360
Jingyuan.

39:35.440 --> 39:36.280
WEI QILIN, HUAIHUA COMMANDANT

39:36.360 --> 39:37.560
The northwest border is harsh and barren.

39:37.640 --> 39:40.440
Jinzhou, Chongzhou, and Jizhou
are especially impoverished.

39:40.960 --> 39:43.080
You must take good care of yourself.

39:44.000 --> 39:46.680
A true man should make his mark,

39:47.200 --> 39:48.960
far better than bowing

39:49.040 --> 39:52.800
and scraping in the capital,
fawning over the powerful.

39:54.160 --> 39:55.000
What a pity.

39:55.600 --> 39:57.600
I won't be here when my nephew is born.

39:57.680 --> 39:58.880
It will be your niece!

39:58.960 --> 40:00.560
You prefer a girl?

40:01.880 --> 40:04.680
Jingyuan, you've read
more books than I have.

40:04.760 --> 40:06.400
Help me pick a name for your niece.

40:06.480 --> 40:10.640
Why don't you let your lord pick a name?

40:10.720 --> 40:12.480
The Commander is too important.

40:12.560 --> 40:14.320
I'm afraid it would overwhelm the child.

40:15.400 --> 40:16.240
Dear Chancellor,

40:16.840 --> 40:19.360
our boy Jiuheng is quite clever.

40:19.440 --> 40:22.680
When will he be able to enter
your Imperial Academy

40:22.760 --> 40:24.040
and study a few books?

40:25.440 --> 40:27.400
Xie Zheng is still a child,

40:27.920 --> 40:28.760
and you're his uncle.

40:28.840 --> 40:31.760
His own father isn't worried yet.

40:31.840 --> 40:33.360
Who says I'm not worried?

40:33.440 --> 40:34.280
You don't know.

40:34.360 --> 40:36.280
This boy is a terror now.

40:36.360 --> 40:37.760
Mischief all day long.

40:37.840 --> 40:38.680
I'm not joking.

40:38.760 --> 40:40.240
I want to send him
to the Imperial Academy right now.

40:40.320 --> 40:42.080
Let you properly educate him.

40:46.200 --> 40:47.160
Changyu.

40:47.240 --> 40:48.440
Changyu?

40:48.520 --> 40:49.360
Yes.

40:50.000 --> 40:51.080
Wei Changyu.

40:51.160 --> 40:52.840
"Long may we bask in grace's light,

40:52.920 --> 40:54.720
where jade steps see
spring grass bloom bright."

40:54.800 --> 40:56.080
How's that?

40:56.840 --> 40:58.000
That's a good name.

40:58.520 --> 41:00.840
When the time comes,
I'll bring her to kowtow to you.

41:05.840 --> 41:07.160
Good wine.

41:07.240 --> 41:09.960
-Good wine.
-Next year, when you leave for Jinzhou,

41:10.560 --> 41:12.080
if the General is willing,

41:12.600 --> 41:13.960
I wish to accompany you.

41:16.680 --> 41:17.960
Together, we'll face the nation's crisis.

41:21.080 --> 41:22.640
Your Highness's safety

41:22.720 --> 41:25.720
concerns the stability
of the court and the realm.

41:25.800 --> 41:27.720
This cannot be taken lightly.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.280
Indeed.

41:29.800 --> 41:32.280
"A prince does not sit
beneath a dangling eaves."

41:33.080 --> 41:34.320
Your Highness, please reconsider.

41:35.320 --> 41:37.120
You may not know.

41:37.640 --> 41:39.800
This summer, floods ravaged the south.

41:40.360 --> 41:42.080
I went to provide relief,

41:42.160 --> 41:44.240
but the Jia family
obstructed me at every turn.

41:44.320 --> 41:46.720
The victims suffered terribly.

41:46.800 --> 41:48.560
My father was furious.

41:49.520 --> 41:50.720
Yet he didn't punish

41:51.240 --> 41:53.640
the Sixteenth Prince or the Jia family.

41:54.240 --> 41:55.760
Instead, he blamed me

41:56.880 --> 41:58.400
for inadequate relief efforts.

42:00.080 --> 42:01.240
All these years,

42:01.760 --> 42:04.680
my father has been harsh with me,

42:05.720 --> 42:08.360
yet lenient with the Jia family

42:09.360 --> 42:10.880
and the Sixteenth Prince.

42:11.880 --> 42:13.760
My heart is lost.

42:15.160 --> 42:16.520
Perhaps,

42:16.600 --> 42:18.760
only by leaving the court,

42:20.320 --> 42:22.080
making my mark at the frontier,

42:23.240 --> 42:26.200
can I

42:26.800 --> 42:28.320
find my way out.

42:38.280 --> 42:40.160
Family affairs.

42:42.600 --> 42:44.080
I've made you…

42:46.040 --> 42:47.360
all laugh.

42:49.600 --> 42:51.720
Your Highness possesses
both benevolence and virtue,

42:51.800 --> 42:53.240
wisdom and courage.

42:53.960 --> 42:56.120
You are the only choice for succession.

42:56.200 --> 42:57.040
I don't understand.

42:57.120 --> 42:59.960
Why is His Majesty so partial?

43:05.400 --> 43:07.640
If the Emperor lacks virtue…

43:11.400 --> 43:13.560
let him abdicate, then.

46:01.120 --> 46:04.240
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:04.320 --> 46:05.200
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
